{"type":"text","timestamp":1775874564971,"sessionID":"ses_285a46612ffe1UhCW63g46pHPD","part":{"id":"prt_d7a5f1c8b0016W3sRthsc56p2n","messageID":"msg_d7a5f080a001RPB0sU0dXNhVW0","sessionID":"ses_285a46612ffe1UhCW63g46pHPD","type":"text","text":"Now I have a complete picture. Let me compile the verification report.\n\n---\n\n## AR-031 RBAC 配置 — Spec Verification Report\n\n### Overall: **PASS with 1 defect**\n\n### Test Results\n- **78/79 tests pass** (the 1 failure `fullnameOverride` is unrelated to AR-031)\n- `helm lint` passes with default values and with all RBAC enabled\n\n### Requirement-by-Requirement Verification\n\n| # | Requirement | Status | Notes |\n|---|-------------|--------|-------|\n| 1 | RBAC directory consolidation | **PASS** | `rbac/` contains `workloadmanager.yaml`, `router.yaml`, `volcano-scheduler.yaml`. `rbac-router.yaml` does not exist at templates root. |\n| 2 | Volcano template retains only non-RBAC | **PASS** | `volcano-agent-scheduler-development.yaml` contains only ConfigMap, Service, Deployment. No SA/CR/CRB. |\n| 3 | WM RBAC values gate | **PASS** | `workloadmanager.rbac.create: true` default. `--set ...=false` renders zero RBAC resources. |\n| 4 | Volcano RBAC values gate | **PASS** | Empty string follows `enabled`; explicit bool overrides. All 4 scenarios verified. |\n| 5 | Router RBAC gate unchanged | **PASS** | Default `false`, enabled with `--set router.rbac.create=true`, custom SA name works. |\n| 6 | ClusterRole naming `agentcube-` prefix | **PASS** | WM: `agentcube-workloadmanager`, Volcano: `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler`. |\n| 7 | Binding naming `-binding` suffix | **PASS** | WM: `agentcube-workloadmanager-binding`, Router: `agentcube-router-binding`, Volcano: `agentcube-volcano-agent-scheduler-binding`. |\n| 8 | SA naming consistency | **PASS** | WM: `workloadmanager`, Router: configurable (default `agentcube-router`), Volcano: `volcano-agent-scheduler`. |\n| 9 | RBAC permissions unchanged | **PASS** | WM: 13 rules match spec exactly. Router: full CRUD on secrets. Volcano: 18 rules match spec. |\n| 10 | Kubernetes standard labels | **PASS (defect)** | Component names correct via YAML last-key-wins, but **duplicate `app.kubernetes.io/name` keys** exist (see defect below). |\n| 11 | `_helpers.tpl` RBAC helpers | **PASS** | `agentcube.rbacName` and `agentcube.rbacBindingName` defined with truncation to 63 chars. |\n| 12 | `values.yaml` RBAC key tree | **PASS** | `workloadmanager.rbac.create: true`, `router.rbac.create: false`, `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create: \"\"`. Missing behavioral comment for volcano key. |\n| 13 | Helm upgrade backward compat | **N/A (structural)** | Helm's native GVK+name tracking handles this. No runtime test possible without a cluster. |\n| 14 | Binding integrity | **PASS** | All bindings correctly reference their Role/SA. Verified via rendered output. |\n| 15 | Helm lint passes | **PASS** | Both default and all-RBAC-enabled scenarios pass with 0 failures. |\n\n### Defect Found\n\n**D-01: Duplicate `app.kubernetes.io/name` labels in RBAC resources**\n\nEach RBAC resource has two `app.kubernetes.io/name` entries:\n```yaml\nlabels:\n  {{- include \"agentcube.labels\" . | nindent 4 }}   # emits app.kubernetes.io/name: agentcube\n  app.kubernetes.io/name: workloadmanager            # component-specific override\n```\n\nYAML last-key-wins means the effective value IS correct (`workloadmanager`, `router`, `volcano-scheduler`), but duplicate keys are:\n- A YAML anti-pattern\n- Could cause issues with strict YAML validators\n- The `agentcube.labels` helper should not be used as-is for RBAC resources, or `selectorLabels` should be excluded\n\n**Fix**: Either exclude `selectorLabels` from RBAC label blocks, or use a labels variant without `app.kubernetes.io/name`.\n\n**D-02 (minor): Missing behavioral comment for `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create`**\n\nSpec requires: \"a comment explains that empty string means the value follows `volcano.scheduler.enabled`\". The `values.yaml` has no such comment for the `volcano.scheduler.rbac.create` key.","time":{"start":1775874564968,"end":1775874564968}}}
